          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Wake Up Call",
            "text": "<p>Get your day off to the best start with a Wake Up Call! Take a sneak peek behind the scenes to see what exciting new products and live guests today’s shows have in store! And you never know who might pop in to chat about what’s coming up, so keep your eyes peeled!</p><p><strong>Monday - Friday 12pm - 1pm UK | 7am - 8am EDT</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CTV_ShowsWake_up_call_780cfc55-6061-4077-a0ff-b0b29c0ce265.jpg"
          }
        },
        "66f1b323-fbfa-4762-99e3-3053d001c1be": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Craft Vault",
            "text": "<p>Unlock the door to a whole world of unmissable deals in the Craft Vault! Join us to turn the key and step into this treasury of treats to discover all of the offers, deals and bargains you can get your hands on</p><p> </p><p><strong>Check our </strong><a href=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\" title=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\"><strong>weekly schedule</strong></a><strong> for show times</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CTV_ShowsThe_craft_vault_0747825e-5656-4872-af25-7d60714631f9.jpg"
          }
        },
        "24072f0b-7fcf-44b9-aabe-21f93572daba": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Craft Along",
            "text": "<p>You’ve got your hands on the newest crafting must-have… now, all you need is the crafty know how! </p><p>Join us for Craft Along where we'll take you on a step-by-step journey filled with tips and techniques to master your latest purchase!</p><p> <strong>Check our</strong><a href=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\" title=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\"><strong> weekly schedule</strong></a><strong> for show times</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CTV_ShowsCraft_along_4800acda-9abe-4b13-aad6-372e3f2be11e.jpg"
          }
        }
      },
