          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Beautiful Beginnings",
            "text": "<p>New to Crafter’s TV, and want to jump straight into some crafting and creativity? Welcome to Beautiful Beginnings! This is the first stage of your craft journey, and we’ll be with you every step of the way with beginner craft techniques, introductions to essential crafting tools and so much fun!</p><p><strong>Check our </strong><a href=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\" title=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\"><strong>weekly schedule</strong></a><strong> for show times</strong></p>",
