        "be996866-a740-448d-9b0d-497d65d97887": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Countdown To Launch",
            "text": "<p>Each jam-packed show will preview all of the exciting and much-anticipated craft collections coming up in the next month.</p><p>This is your exclusive opportunity to take a first look at our upcoming papercraft, art and sewing goodies, discover something new and reignite your creative imagination. </p><p><strong>Check our </strong><a href=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\" title=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\"><strong>weekly schedule</strong></a><strong> for show times</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Countdown_To_Launch_14d47454-a9c0-4cbd-9554-2db05eb1f413.jpg"
          }
        },
        "8048bc5b-d6f2-4cb7-8791-e3ec2a844270": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Friday Night Live",
            "text": "<p>Join us every Friday for a recap of all the best products and deals from the week. Expect interactive demonstrations, new studio games, and plenty of live surprises, plus all that feel-good Crafter’s TV energy you know and love to take you into the weekend. </p><p><strong>Fridays - 5pm - 7pm UK | 12pm - 2pm EDT</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Friday_Night_Live_3a726c64-7886-4645-95a0-4ec955d302fd.jpg"
          }
        },
