          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "small_heading": "",
            "heading": "Craft Your Stash",
            "text": "<p>Ready for a fresh creative perspective? </p><p>Take a new look at your crafting collection to make something unique or try a new technique.</p><p><strong>Check our </strong><a href=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\" title=\"https://crafters-uk.myshopify.com/pages/crafters-tv-schedule\"><strong>weekly schedule</strong></a><strong> for show times</strong></p>",
